{"tid":504944,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人三日唔埋兩日就想死","createTime":"2017-12-20T15:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T09:50:38.000Z","uid":126615,"like":87,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"31fc244b7b6d368356d98bde5edbf569114ce4da","tid":504944,"uid":126615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T15:00:14.000Z","msg":"有時 我真係懷疑自己係咪憂鬱<br />\n覺得呢個世界冇哂希望 grad左又唔知可以做咩 冇一樣自己真正嘅興趣<br />\n朋友我有嘅 不過通常佢地通常唔會認同我 所以有咩事都唔會同人講<br />\n一行出街有人望我就會諗佢地係咪喺度恥笑我<br />\n而家sem break唔洗出街就喺屋企訓成日 醒左就係咁諗死<br />\n就黎頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"979020eca145778efcd932e8eebaf84a046395bd","tid":504944,"uid":25044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T15:08:00.000Z","msg":"唔洗兩日 一停低就想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf284a3c506fcf4158a15438f2d31780461895e","tid":504944,"uid":126615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T15:11:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗兩日 一停低就想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我都係停低就想"},{"pid":"239be9ed68a598615eb70e7c8782bb1578e597f2","tid":504944,"uid":6067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T15:12:43.000Z","msg":"呢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但唔捨得屋企人haha"},{"pid":"3c4d5fef13dc018fec88220242b2f45d984ec1a9","tid":504944,"uid":160363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T15:20:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dadb01684a8c9f0eeb3730ab3c6a619aa83559cd","tid":504944,"uid":126615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T15:32:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但唔捨得屋企人haha</blockquote><br />\n如果唔係死後嗰知未知嘅恐懼 我神早就死左"},{"pid":"415b09d4968ec20ba452be053b7b3567845e2385","tid":504944,"uid":14605,"like":2,"dislike"