ockquote><br />\n不要放棄生命，想想你的父母</blockquote><br />\n就係屋企人對我差</blockquote><br />\n點差？願閒其詳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老豆疑似自殺<br />\n阿媽話鍊死我好過養到我咁大"},{"pid":"7d2436479f8e52c74195a7c863c4f9a6269a87c5","tid":504944,"uid":48903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:06:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時 我真係懷疑自己係咪憂鬱<br />\n覺得呢個世界冇哂希望 grad左又唔知可以做咩 冇一樣自己真正嘅興趣<br />\n朋友我有嘅 不過通常佢地通常唔會認同我 所以有咩事都唔會同人講<br />\n一行出街有人望我就會諗佢地係咪喺度恥笑我<br />\n而家sem break唔洗出街就喺屋企訓成日 醒左就係咁諗死<br />\n就黎頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁"},{"pid":"109990c42971b8b67f80eb05e461cdb0f424e053","tid":504944,"uid":22227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:07:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89277df1b49fa24b40861d670e7cd5d24afb6ff4","tid":504944,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:10:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n至少你還活著同我談話，即係代表你已經三餐不憂有一個有瓦遮頭既地方，這是其中一個得到既例子😝</blockquote><br />\n我想安樂死多d</blockquote><br />\n不要放棄生命，想想你的父母</blockquote><br />\n就係屋企人對我差</blockquote><br />\n點差？願閒其詳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老豆疑似自殺<br />\n阿媽話鍊死我好過養到我咁大</blockquote><br />\n疑似自殺？死左？阿媽可能係氣話？嬲既時候講既野唔可以算數，不要太認真。</blockquote><br />\n1.死咗<br />\n2.阿媽係在我被人害想攞番公道時鬧我，唔可能係氣話"},{"pid":"9fec65d1ab128e256017e727d505496fb2bbc4bf","tid":504944,"uid":22227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:16:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"849480a28f0305aea8122d0a584bd65766740587","tid":504944,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:22:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n不要放棄生命，想想你的父母</blockquote><br />\n就係屋企人對我差</blockquote><br />\n點差？願閒其詳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile